{"id":162053,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/yahoo奇摩-黑心土產店-洋鹿茸坑中國客-民視/","date":"2011-06-17T14:30:19Z","modified":"2011-06-17T14:30:19Z","title":"Yahoo!奇摩 | 黑心土產店 洋鹿茸坑中國客 (民視)","content":"<div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://tw.news.yahoo.com/photo/url/d/i/110617/11/20110617_4616005/20110617_4616005.jpg.html\"><img src=\"http://l.yimg.com/o/xp/ftv/20110617/22/45626290.jpg\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p>很多觀光區，都有鏢客兜售鹿茸，小心睜大眼睛！南投檢警大掃蕩，<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://tw.news.yahoo.com/article/url/d/a/110617/11/2ti86.html\" title=\"日月潭\"><span>日月潭</span></a>有3家黑心土產店，勾結旅行社坑殺中國遊客，以低價進口紐西蘭鹿茸，冒充本土鹿茸，獲取暴利。</p>\n<p>檢警搜索日月潭的3家山產店，搜出來的一根一根鹿茸，以及這一陀一陀紅紅的假鹿胎，都是從紐西蘭進口的廉價品，店員推銷時卻謊稱是台灣野生水鹿，哄抬價格，訛詐觀光客。</p>\n<p>這些「肉店」，現在不鏢散客，改鏢整團，直接坑殺「羊群」，特產店會和旅行社簽約分帳，導遊負責帶人來，平常店門緊閉，遊覽車一到，才會拉開鐵門，安排解說，檢警掃蕩黑心店，取締非法，但負面形象，卻讓合法商店無辜受創。</p>\n<p>紐西蘭鹿茸，其實功效差不多，外觀也很像，只是店家低買高賣，5斤就3萬<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://tw.news.yahoo.com/article/url/d/a/110617/11/2ti86.html\" title=\"台幣\"><span>台幣</span></a>，人工栽種的靈芝，也誆稱是野生靈芝，身價翻了又翻，台灣民眾自己要張大眼睛，檢警更要不定期查緝，杜絕死灰復燃。</p>\n</p></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.rd.yahoo.com%2Freferurl%2Fnews%2Frss%2Fintl%2F%2Ahttp%253A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Farticle%2Furl%2Fd%2Fa%2F110617%2F11%2F2ti86.html&#038;title=%E9%BB%91%E5%BF%83%E5%9C%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%BA%97+%E6%B4%8B%E9%B9%BF%E8%8C%B8%E5%9D%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A2+%28%E6%B0%91%E8%A6%96%29\">Chat about this 